            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Welcome. Want to try some delicious food?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Huh? That voice is..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "It is very, very delicious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I knew it, Linca. Why are you soliciting for this place?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha... There is a complex set of circumstances behind this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "A while back, I followed a delicious smell back to this store."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x166,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Then, I do not know the name of it, but it was coming from a most delicious looking grilled meat..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x166,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I ordered one, but when I finished eating, I realized that I had forgotten my wallet."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x167,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "For that reason, I have to work off the amount of money I owe for the food I ate."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I-I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "U-Umm, if you don't mind, I could pay for you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x194,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I cannot accept that. Marion tells me that I must hold myself accountable for my actions."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "But, if you insist...it would be of great help if you teach me how to solicit."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Ehh! I-I've never done it, either..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd3,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "So you cannot...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "*sigh* Don't look at me with those<CR>puppy-dog eyes... Okay, I can try."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "U-Umm...anyone want delicious food...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I see. I will use that as a reference."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "U-Umm, anyone want delicious food...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Welcome. Please come in."
